description: Removes tags from an EFS resource. You can remove tags from EFS file systems and access points using this API operation. This operation requires permissions for the elasticfilesystem:UntagResource action.

parameters.name: ResourceId
parameters.description: Specifies the EFS resource that you want to remove tags from.

parameters.name: TagKeys
parameters.description: The keys of the key-value tag pairs that you want to remove from the specified EFS resource. (string) ---
